dc_title_s: Westmorlandia, Lancastria, Cestria, Caernarvan, Denbigh, Flint, Merionidh, Montgomery, Salopia/ cum Insulis Mania et Anglesey.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Includes illustrations of ships on the ocean. From the Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt. 1 map: 54x 44 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
